column16: Jake Lamb grounds into a double play, second baseman Cory Spangenberg to shortstop Chase d'Arnaud to first baseman Jose Pirela.   Daniel Descalso out at 2nd.
Brandon Drury flies out to right fielder Hunter Renfroe.   Chris Owings to 3rd.
Chris Herrmann grounds out, third baseman Ryan Schimpf to first baseman Hector Sanchez.
